description: Commercial Encryption Library for .NET.  Features: Encrypt strings, files, & streams, Symmetric Encryption (AES, Twofish, Blowfish, DES, TripleDES, RC2), Asymmetric Encryption (RSA, X509 Certificate), hashing (SHA, MD, FCS, HAVAL, Ripemd, Whirlpool, Tiger, Gost), compression (gzip, deflate) and  encoding (uuEncode, quoted printable, Hex String).
releaseNotes: Kellerman Software announces a major update to the .NET Encryption Library. The help file has been completely reworked with numerous examples. Other new features include MiniLZO compression, CRC32 for streams, and Adler32 for streams.
